{
  "stem": "25178.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we tried to talk him out of it because she had-- he only had known her for about a month or two months, he didn't know her too well.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told him, be careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he married her anyhow because the reason he got married, he was being transferred back to the mainland here and they were going to station him in Idaho, Mountain Home Air Force Base.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he didn't want to leave her behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he married her, in May of 1978.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in July of 1978, he was transferred to Mountain Home Air Force Base.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he was in the process of being checked in and he rented a place on the base.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on his way to Idaho with his wife to buy furniture, on a Saturday morning, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] he was hit head-on by another oncoming car, and a drunk driver.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 17 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Killed him instantly, and his wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] We had his body flown over to Los Angeles for a funeral.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And he had a military funeral with military honors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother came to attend the funeral.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because he said he wanted to say, good bye, or honor Fred.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My thought always was he should've done it while he was alive, which he didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the only thing my brother could say to me after the funeral was, Jack, hang in there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then he left, and I haven't seen him since.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My son's death [PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] affected the whole family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My wife, Juliet, she treated him like her own son.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CRYING] Olivia, it was her big brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
